body told me—yes, Tobak!—that Lucette is at the Alphonse Four. I haven’t asked you about your father? He’s in good health?” (Van bowed.) “And how is the guvernantka belletristka?”

“Her last novel is called L’ami Luc. She just got the Lebon Academy Prize for her copious rubbish.”

They parted laughing.

